{"tid":2311723,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★海洋公園男職員患哮喘、氣管炎　廁內暈倒送院亡","createTime":"2020-12-04T09:53:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T10:16:38.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a57db0c40381b70911968a1906bd18f7b520d87d","tid":2311723,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T09:53:09.000Z","msg":"昨日（3日）下午5時許，警方接獲保安員報案，指一名60歲姓盧男職員於海洋公園行政大樓的男廁廁格內暈倒昏迷。警員及救護員接報到場，將傷者送往瑪麗醫院搶救，惟最終證實死亡。據知，死者患有哮喘及氣管炎至少半年以上。<br />\n<br />\n海洋公園證實死者為香港海洋公園保育基金（保育基金）的兼職員工，並對事件深表沉痛，指已聯絡事主家人及作最深切慰問，並會全力提供最適切協助。<br />\n<br />\n勞工處回應指，處方已知悉事件，並已派員到意外現場了解及就意外原因展開調查<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/557485/%E6%B5%B7%E6%B4%8B%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92%E7%94%B7%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E6%82%A3%E5%93%AE%E5%96%98-%E6%B0%A3%E7%AE%A1%E7%82%8E-%E5%BB%81%E5%85%A7%E6%9A%88%E5%80%92%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2%E4%BA%A1-%E5%9C%92%E6%96%B9%E6%B7%B1%E8%A1%A8%E6%B2%89%E7%97%9B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F557485%2F%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E6%25B4%258B%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%259C%2592%25E7%2594%25B7%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%2582%25A3%25E5%2593%25AE%25E5%2596%2598-%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%25BB%2581%25E5%2585%25A7%25E6%259A%2588%25E5%2580%2592%25E9%2580%2581%25E9%2599%25A2%25E4%25BA%25A1-%25E5%259C%2592%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%25B2%2589%25E7%2597%259B&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGHQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=12cd4b16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/557485/%E6%B5%B7%E6%B4%8B%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92%E7%94%B7%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E6%82%A3%E5%93%AE%E5%96%98-%E6%B0%A3%E7%AE%A1%E7%82%8E-%E5%BB%81%E5%85%A7%E6%9A%88%E5%80%92%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2%E4%BA%A1-%E5%9C%92%E6%96%B9%E6%B7%B1%E8%A1%A8%E6%B2%89%E7%97%9B</a>"},{"pid":"231e33936edd1c5fbbced488a72a3fa2432513db","tid":2311723,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T09:53:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/